        "TileImage": "$($repository 3e3e3752-37db-4b0f-8ff3-827d4c565e55).Image",
        "Description": "Long time no see, 47\r\rAfter ICA downfall, we still have 2 more enemies to take down, but first you need to kill 4 targets, sebastian sato, Marcus and Cornelia Stuyvesant and Lucy Phillips. Sebastian, Marcus and Lucy are judges for near garden event in Dartmoon, and our client has bad past with all of them. We also eliminate marcus, becuese our client and him are bussines enemies. In exchange, he will gives us more intel about rico delgado cartel. Good Hunting 47\r\r- Mr. Axo",
